title: path/filepath: TestWinSplitListTestsAreValid execution error
body:
What steps will reproduce the problem?
1. Update to latest Go tip
2. Build Go

What is the expected output?

go version devel +f002e89cbd51 Wed Feb 27 15:19:23 2013 +1100 windows/386

Best regards,
Dobrosław Żybort
